channel.title: Duplicate label error?
channel.description: ok, i got a duplicate label error, because i added a staff id to give unlimited runes to 7 different rune types, i know what it means, but is there anyway i can make the staff have all 7 runes as infinity ingame (like air staff has infinity air runes) for the same staff, can someone tell me how?

item.title: Duplicate label error?
item.dc:creator: @EmulousGuru EmulousGuru
item.description:
@EmulousGuru wrote:

Yes, use one case and append an variable for each part.
Such as;

case 1234:
    if (newVariable == 1) {
        /* method
        * for no
        * runes
        */
    } else {
        /* normal
        * method
        * for staff
        */
    }
break;

That should give you an idea.
